      <title>意大利经受住了标准普尔对梅洛尼恶化债务轨迹的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/italy-survives-s-p-scrutiny-of-meloni-s-worsened-debt-trajectory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级机构对意大利的信用状况保持不变，该评级机构对总理乔治亚·梅洛尼政府预见到的债务恶化轨迹进行了首次重大审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/italy-survives-s-p-scrutiny-of-meloni-s-worsened-debt-trajectory</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 10:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>绘制全球经济图：美联储延迟重新调整所有利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/world-economy-latest-fed-s-delay-to-cut-recalibrates-all-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，在一系列令人惊讶的高通胀数据减少了全球宽松政策的空间后，美国央行官员将等待更长的时间来削减借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/world-economy-latest-fed-s-delay-to-cut-recalibrates-all-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国家石油公司董事会同意派发 50% 的股息，结束争议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/petrobras-asks-investors-to-approve-50-payout-of-extra-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Petroleo Brasileiro SA 董事会决定从 2023 年起支付其潜在特别股息的 50%，解决了因总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 对这家国家控制的石油生产商施加过多影响而引发的一场震动巴西市场的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/petrobras-asks-investors-to-approve-50-payout-of-extra-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
